entries.femaleVariant: The scopsucking bastard...! Fire my daughter! My little girl!
Shhh, quiet, they'll hear you... I mean, there's rules...
I don't give a fuck about their rules, their stupid wars...! Can't even follow those rules, you can't!
A person's gotta eat, gotta work, gotta have implants to even hold down a job!
And what, the girl's gotta turn up her nose if some 6th Street offers her a gig on the side?
Well... she coulda asked the Tinos for help. It's their turf, they got a right to be mad.
Just be glad they just tossed her outta the bar. They could've... Well, you know. Could've been worse.
